ABC (Liquor Licenses).meetings: every third Wednesday at the Thurgood Marshall Center, 7:00 p.m.
ABC (Liquor Licenses).purpose: The ABC Committee reviews and recommends action to the Commission on all issues affecting liquor, restaurant, retail and entertainment licenses.

Design Review.meetings: every third Monday at the Thurgood Marshall Center, 7:00 p.m.
Design Review.purpose: The Design Review Committee reviews all applications and proposals relating to development, design, historic preservation and zoning.

Grants.purpose:
The Grants Committee reviews applications from community organizations for grants from ANC 1B to support worthy projects. Persons or organizations interested in applying for a grant should 
contact the Commissioner representing their single-member district for 
assistance and support.

Public Safety.purpose: The committee reviews all issues affecting public safety and law enforcement in ANC 1B and recommends actions to the Commission when appropriate.

Transportation.meetings: every third Thursday at the Thurgood Marshall Center, 7:00 p.m.
Transportation.purpose: The Transportation Committee reviews all applications and proposals relating to transportation, parking and other similar topics.
